	<h1>COVID-19 Information</h1>
<hr>
<p class="bodyText" align="left">This page will be used to house all OCS information pertaining to the COVID-19 West Virginia Schools' Closing. The page will be updated as new information becomes available.</p>
<h4 align="left">Instruction Information</h4>
<p>PreK through 5th Grade Instructional Materials/Assignments:  <a href="https://sites.google.com/wphs.ohio.k12.wv.us/elementary-instruction/home">Click Here</a> Instructional Plan Information: <a href="http://boe.ohio.k12.wv.us/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2020/03/prek5-instruction-info.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Click here</a></p>
<p>Middle through High School Information: <a href="http://boe.ohio.k12.wv.us/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2020/03/middle-high-instruction-info.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Click here</a></p>
<h4 align="left">Food Service</h4>
<p align="left">Meal Locations: Meals will be served from 11:00am to 1:00pm, on Fridays. Click link for Site Information Flyer: <a href="http://boe.ohio.k12.wv.us/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2020/04/meal_locations_4-17.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener">School Sites</a>   <a href="http://boe.ohio.k12.wv.us/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2020/04/meal_mobile-4-17.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mobile Sites</a></p>
<h4 align="left">Contact Us</h4>
<p align="left">Currently, non-essential school personnel are not reporting to their schools.  This means that there may not be anyone available to take your phone call at your child's school.  Please contact the Ohio County School's Board of Education Office at 304.243.0300 and they will assist you any way they can.</p>
